                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "36fae90c-82f8-4597-9669-7f280c300fc6"
                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "87e113b4061c4a9c937e0",
                    "stepText": "Next, compute the rotational kinetic energy. Using the moment of inertia from step 2 and the relation from step 3, determine the rotational energy $!$\\frac{1}{2}I\\omega^2$!$.",
